name: 比安卡·贝克尔斯-罗斯
name_full: 比安卡·贝克尔斯-罗斯 Bianca Beckles-Rose
introduction: Bianca Beckles-Rose is alum of The BRIT School of Performing Arts in the United Kingdom, South London where she studied Musical Theatre. She has worked passionately as creative developer and producer for scripted projects and has notable musical, dramatic and comedic performances spanning live concert orchestras, British theatre, and international filmed productions.
